SportsMEDIA Technology Corporation: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 5:06 PM ET
Electronic Equipment, Instruments and Components

Company Overview of SportsMEDIA Technology Corporation



Snapshot People




Company Overview
SportsMEDIA Technology Corporation delivers solutions for live sports and entertainment events globally. It offers clock and score, race crawl, ticker, virtual golf, virtual enhancement, virtual studio, tracking, and interactive touch products; and video production, data and graphics integration, data operations center, help desk support, onsite staffing and operation, and design studio services. The company was founded in 1988 and is based in Durham, North Carolina with a location in Jacksonville, Florida.


3511 University DriveDurham, NC 27707United StatesFounded in 1988



Phone: 919-493-9390

Fax: 919-493-7782

www.smt.com







