Company Profile
Sector: Communications
Industry: Media
Sub-Industry: Publishing & Broadcasting
Sportsmedia Technology Corp offers real-time delivery of data and social media for live television sports and entertainment TV. The Company designs clocks and score boards, race crawls, virtual insertion products, tickers, and stand alone graphics for live television sports and entertainment TV.




