About
Sportsmedia Technology Corp is located at the address 3511 University Dr in Durham, North Carolina 27707.  They can be contacted via phone at (919) 493-9390 for pricing, hours and directions.  Sportsmedia Technology Corp has an annual sales volume of 5M – 9,999,999.  .For more information contact Sports  Media,  or  go to www.sportsmedia.comSportsmedia Technology Corp provides On-Site Services, Customer Service, Diagnostics to it's customers.  For maps and directions to Sportsmedia Technology Corp view the map to the right.  For reviews of Sportsmedia Technology Corp see below.









